### 5.2 Component Design Patterns

**Pattern 1: Data-Driven Components**
```tsx
// Component nhận data từ file TypeScript
<PricingTable data={service.content.pricing} />
<FAQAccordion data={service.content.faq} />
```

**Pattern 2: Composition Pattern**
```tsx
// Homepage compose từ nhiều components
export default function Home() {
  return (
    <>
      <HeroSection />
      <PainPointSection />
      <EducationSection />
      <StatsSection />
      <ServicesGrid />
      <ProcessSection />
      // ... 5 sections khác
    </>
  );
}
```

**Pattern 3: Reusable Section Components**
```tsx
// Cùng 1 component dùng cho nhiều pages
<FinalCTA variant="landing" />     // Landing pages
<FinalCTA variant="services" />    // Services index
<FinalCTA variant="blog" />        // Blog posts
```

